face global LineNumbers black,white
face global LineNumberCursor black,white+r
face global MenuForeground black,white+fgiru
face global MenuBackground black,white
face global MenuInfo black,white+fgir
face global Information black,white+fgir
face global Error black,white+cfgiu
face global StatusLine black,white
face global StatusLineMode black,white+r
face global StatusLineInfo black,white+r
face global StatusLineValue black,white+r
